                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable H</hi> 91.) I saw the prisoner asleep in Vi<lb></lb>negar-fields, Poplar, about twelve o'clock in the day—I found 9 1/2 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>. on him, and 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. in silver—I should say he had been drinking.</p>
